### State Reset on Close In Widget.jsx, resetSelections() is called inside handleClose. If a user accidentally closes the widget or clicks outside, they lose their selected network and token.

### Fix: Consider resetting state only on successful transaction completion, not just on UI closure, to improve User Experience.

